These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, engineer, bartender, lawyer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, hip-hop, d&b, gospel
1. the lawyer is on the left of the mechanic##1
2. the mechanic is on the right of the lawyer##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left or far right##3
4. the bartender is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
5. the fan of gospel is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of d&b##2
6. the lawyer is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Job   | lawyer | mechanic     | bartender | engineer |
| Music-Genre     | salsa     | d&b | gospel  | hip-hop      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, sudoku, card-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy, dahlia, amaryllis
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
6. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Hobby   | dancing | drawing    | card-games     | sudoku  |
| Flower     | sunflower    | dahlia | poppy | amaryllis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different games are played: poker, snooker, mah-jongg, go
House: colonial, cape-cod, gothic-revival, tower
1. the tower house is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
2. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the colonial house is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Game   | snooker   | mah-jongg   | poker  | go |
| House           | cape-cod | tower | gothic-revival | colonial  |

