.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, domino, billiard, canasta
4 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, turtle, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the person playing monopoly and the owner of the turtle##2
3. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Game         | domino | monopoly | canasta | billiard  |
| Pet   | hamster  | bird   | lizard  | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, july, october
4 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, hamster, ferret
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the owner of the ferret is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Birthday   | september    | january   | july | october    |
| Pet      | hedgehog | frog | hamster       | ferret |

