.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, blue, black, green
There 4 different types of food: peach, grapefruit, carrot, avocado
1. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes black##1
2. the person eating carrot is between the person eating avocado and the person who likes black##2
3. the person eating peach is between the person eating carrot and the person who likes chestnut##2
4. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Color    | chestnut | black | green | blue |
| Food   | grapefruit | peach  | carrot    | avocado  |

