.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, purple, ivory, aquamarine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, punk, salsa, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
4. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes aquamarine##2
5. the fan of punk is the fan of punk##1
6. the fan of punk is between the fan of salsa and the person who likes aquamarine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Color   | mauve | aquamarine | ivory | purple     |
| Music-Genre     | reggae | jazz  | punk   | salsa |

