.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, swimming, parkour, water-polo
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, funk, reggae, punk
1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is the fan of funk##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Sport         | water-polo | parkour | sailing | swimming   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | reggae | r&b      | punk |

