.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, bongani, dannemann, chaman
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, canasta, go
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing go is on the far right##1
3. the person playing go is the chaman-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bongani-smoker is between the person playing chess and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar     | alhambra | bongani   | dannemann      | chaman      |
| Game   | chess     | canasta | monopoly | go |

