.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, june, july
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, montecristo, prince, chaman
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is between the chaman-smoker and the montecristo-smoker##2
3. the person who's birthday is in november is the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the prince-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Birthday   | february | november | june      | july   |
| Cigar   | prince  | montecristo    | fonseca | chaman |

