2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the colonial house##1
3. the wooden house is the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
5. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
6. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre       | fantasy | drama | sports    | crime      |
| House   | cape-cod       | wooden       | colonial | modern |

