.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, card-games, video-games, magic-tricks
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, september, november
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | baking | video-games  | magic-tricks | card-games |
| Birthday           | september     | november | october    | may     |

