.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, milk, mirinda
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, family, satire, zombie
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda        | soy-milk       | milk   | almond-milk |
| Movie-Genre    | zombie | satire | family | thriller  |

