.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, september, may
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, pear, kiwi, plum
1. the person eating kiwi is on the far right##1
2. the person eating plum is the person eating plum##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
4. the person eating asparagus is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
6. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Birthday   | april     | march     | september          | may |
| Food      | asparagus | pear | plum | kiwi  |

 